Park Avenue, north from 55th Street, showing the Rits Tower apartments on N. E. corner of S7th Street. The South Kensington (No. 441) Apartments on the N. E. corner of 56th Street, as well as the small building. on the S. E. corner, are old, dating beck to the 1880's. 1932.

Ewing Galloway, Photographer.
